OL,3,CThree arrested after man knocked down
OL,4,Cbefore car crashes into wall
OL,6,FThree people have been arrested after
OL,7,Fa pedestrian was knocked down and
OL,8,Fkilled near to a bus stop.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,Fcrash on Colne Road in Brierfield,
OL,12,FLancashire, on Sunday night, 31 March,
OL,13,Fat around 8.30pm.
OL,15,FIt was established that a BMW M5 had
OL,16,Fstruck a pedestrian and then collided
OL,17,Fwith a wall, close to a bus stop. A
OL,18,Fman in his 50s was found unresponsive
OL,19,Fand was later pronounced dead at the
OL,20,Fscene.
