OL,3,CThree arrested after man knocked down
OL,4,Cbefore car crashes into wall
OL,6,FThree men in total have been arrested
OL,7,Fin connection with the incident.JA 28-
OL,8,Fyear-old man from Brierfield and a 40-
OL,9,Fyear-old man from Manchester were both
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,11,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,13,FA third suspect, a 34-year-old man
OL,14,Ffrom Brierfield, was later also on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,16,Fdangerous driving.
OL,18,FAll three men have since been released
OL,19,Fon bail pending further enquiries.
