OL,3,CThree arrested after man knocked down
OL,4,Cbefore car crashes into wall
OL,6,FSgt Michael Higginson, of our Road
OL,7,FPolicing Unit, said: "This collision
OL,8,Fhas resulted in a man losing his life
OL,9,Fand my thoughts are very much with his
OL,10,Floved ones at this difficult time.
OL,12,F"Although we have made two arrests,
OL,13,Four enquiries are very much ongoing to
OL,14,Festablish what led to the collision
OL,15,Fand identify everyone involved.
